summary:
I am a highly motivated and dedicated junior data analyst driven by desire to uncover insights and trends within complex data sets. I have a strong foundation in programming with Python and am proficient in tools such as Excel, Power BI and Tableau. 

I enjoy working on personal projects that involve web scraping, analysis and data visualization, as it allows me to gain insight further improve my skills. My ultimate goal is to become a data engineer, being at the forefront of data and leading the way in utilizing data to make strategic business decisions.
